==English==

===Noun===
'''filament'''
# a [[fine]] [[thread]] or [[wire]]
# such a wire, heated to [[glowing]], in an [[incandescent]] [[light bulb]] or a [[thermionic valve]]
#{{botany}} The stalk of a [[stamen]] in a [[flower]], supporting the [[anther]].

